      "content": "counselors wont help. they just tell me to manage my time better or do breathing exercises like that actually fixes the fact that my life is a mess. honestly... i just feel like if i could just stop, everything would finally be quiet. if i could just make it all end, i wouldn't have to feel this way anymore.",
